Rokmann



Minneapolis, Minnesota





Level 5  Contributor 


92 reviews 


42 restaurant reviews





36 helpful votes 





“Had Some Beers on the Deck”


Reviewed May 7, 2017




HopFusion brews beer/ale.We were at HopFusion with my cousin and her husband. We had a couple of beers out on the deck. The weather was nice, the beers were good, it was a fun time. It was easy to talk and relax.We did not have any food. I don't even know if they serve food. I think they allow guests to bring food to eat on the deck with their beers (but check with the staff before you try it).I would go back.





Visited March 2017



Value





Service



Food






