 Proud to represent Fort Worth at the 2017 U.S. Open Beer Championship.Cheers to the entire HopFusion team for bringing home some medal!Feisty Blonde - Silver   ~  Fur Slipper - Silver   ~  Hairpin - BronzeCheers also to our friends in NTX who brought home awards. 
 



  
 
 
 

 



  
 
 
 

PRODUCTION BREWERY | TAPROOM | DEEP IN THE HEART OF THE NEAR SOUTHSIDEHi. We're HopFusion Ale Works, a micro-craft brewery in Fort Worth, Texas.Our passions run deep and far − the outdoors, cycling, the arts, metal work, local food, good friends, friendly dogs and, yes, fine craft brew. We’ve discovered along the way that craft beer isn’t about a product or even a brand. It's about community and friends. At its core, craft beer is about the experience.We are lucky to be a part of a vibrant community that supports locally-owned businesses and are honored to have the opportunity to share our passion.We hope you join us on this journey.Want to see and hear who and what HopFusion is - Check this outCheers! 
 




  
 
 
 

OUR TAPROOM IS NOW OPEN!18 months in the making, our unique taproom and brewery is finally open. Climate-controlled, huge 16'x9' HDTV screen, live entertainment, large outdoor patio with great views of downtown Fort Worth - we think it's the perfect setting to experience the unique brews created right behind our 20-tap bar.Our taproom features our 4 annual brews (the signature series) along with a rotating selection of limited quantity experimental brews that can only be found right here.TAPROOM HOURS:MON - closedTUE - THURS - 4 - 11 pmFRI - noon - 11 pmSAT - noon - midnightSUN - noon - 11 pmSee our TapRoom events - here 
 



  
 
 
NOW ON-TAP IN THE TAPROOM!Our taproom offers both production (wide availability - annual) brews as well as limited release/experimentals that can be found only at the brewery.Signature Series:Feisty Blonde - Honey Vanilla BlondeHairpin - Rye Pale AleSteampipe - Black Rye IPAFur Slipper - Imperial Milk StoutClick here for details on each Signature Series brew.Taproom Only - Experimental:A rotating, ever-changing selection of brews envisioned and created right here in the Near Southside on our experimental 2 BBL system.Taproom only brews are limited quantity and subject to change.Click here for details on our experimental brews. 



  
 
 
 
   
 
 

 
 
 































