About




  
 
 
 

Creativity is at the heart of everything we do at HopFusion Ale Works. We are excited by innovation and art, and we decided to fuse those concepts into our brewery.Our founders, Macy Moore and Matt Hill, are passionate about both. They firmly believe that craft brew is an experience, not just a beer. It’s about community and friends. And, they feel that providing a forum for the arts at the brewery brings that experience alive.Macy and Matt both began their award-winning craft brew journey as home brewers, with over a decade of experience between them. Macy developed a passion for the art of light-bodied ales, while Matt’s passion tends towards the darker-bodied ales and barleywines.In a nutshell, HopFusion Ale Works is about good friends, fantastic art, enjoying the ride of life (preferably on a bicycle)…and great craft beer. 
 



  
 
 

Taproom Hours: MON - closedTUE - THURS - 4 - 11 pmFRI - noon - 11 pmSAT - noon - midnightSUN - noon - 11 pm 
 

HopFusion Ale Works, LLCLocation:200 E Broadway Ave  Fort Worth, Texas 76104 info@hopfusionaleworks.com 682-402-9254Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/hopfusionTwitter: https://twitter.com/HopFusionAleInstagram: https://instagram.com/hopfusion_ale_works/  
 

   
 
 
 
 
 

 
 
 




























